<commentInRDBMS><![CDATA[Credit card debt comprises credit granted to households or non-financial corporations either via delayed debit cards, i.e. cards providing convenience credit as defined below, or via credit cards, i.e. cards providing convenience credit and extended credit. Credit card debt is recorded on dedicated card accounts and therefore not evident on current or overdraft accounts. (Regulation (EU) 2021/379, Annex 2)]]></commentInRDBMS>
